com.bigdata.btree.raba.codec

Interface ICodedRaba

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IRaba, Iterable<byte[]>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCodedRaba, CanonicalHuffmanRabaCoder.CodedRabaImpl

    public interface ICodedRaba
extends IRaba
    Interface for an coded logical byte[][]. Implementations of this interface MUST be thread-safe since the B+Tree guarantees the ability to perform concurrent read operations and instances of this interface are used to code the keys and values of B+Tree nodes and leaves.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
